# Type: feat|fix|docs|style|refactor|test|chore|perf|build|ci
# Scope: component|area affected (optional)
# Subject: imperative, present tense, lowercase, no period, max 50 chars
#
# Body: explain what and why (not how), max 72 chars per line
#
# Footer: breaking changes, issue references
# BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
# Closes #123, Fixes #456
#
# Examples:
# feat(auth): add OAuth2 integration
# fix(ui): resolve button alignment on mobile
# docs: update installation instructions
# refactor(parser): simplify tokenization logic
# test(utils): add unit tests for date helpers
# chore(deps): update dependencies to latest versions